nodes.text: The Kwymar Sector Forces, also known as the Kwymar Sector Fleet, were the Galactic Republic's Planetary Security Forces for the Kwymar sector.
The Kwymar Sector Forces was active before the Clone Wars. Wullf Yularen served as a captain in the unit, before resigning and entering the Senate Bureau of Intelligence.

Author Jason Fry introduced the Kwymar Sector Fleet in The Clone Wars: The Official Episode Guide: Season 1, published in October 2009. He also referenced a "Kwymar Sector Forces" in The Essential Guide to Warfare, released in April 2012, and later clarified that they were intended to be the same unit.
